{"tid":2130402,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"北大教授諷紅三代︰不愛江山愛美國","createTime":"2020-07-29T07:38:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T09:04:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4f24e0eb14167ead57a77b32742b2d5f9fb0db33","tid":2130402,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:38:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/china/20200729/AWXXYMCXMSMHZVRWQKB2SM33UY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200729%2FAWXXYMCXMSMHZVRWQKB2SM33UY%2F&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6YhgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=b015c5eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200729%2FAWXXYMCXMSMHZVRWQKB2SM33UY%2F&h=f5774ed1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/china/20200729/AWXXYMCXMSMHZVRWQKB2SM33UY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n北大教授諷紅三代︰不愛江山愛美國<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/PM2XEtWP0O0YCj5d5fXLgkOv9BE=/640x409/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IQSF5SZLXKIUFRWUUJLZQMTEGM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPM2XEtWP0O0YCj5d5fXLgkOv9BE%3D%2F640x409%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIQSF5SZLXKIUFRWUUJLZQMTEGM.jpg&h=eb65cfb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n北大敢言教授鄭也夫不時批評時政。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n「保江山」是中共總書記習近平念茲在茲的事，。。。。。。。。。。。的子孫坐江山的慾望弱化，取而代之是移民海外的願望」，還意有所指揶揄中共特權階層的子孫都用腳投票，「不愛江山愛美國」。<br />\n<br />\n鄭也夫這篇題為《為誰保江山》上周六（25日）在多個網站轉載。文章開。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「壓得住臣民 阻不了子孫」<br />\n<br />\n文章指出，紅色貴族不願坐江山的原因有四。一是中國的自然與社會環境的極度惡化，包括失去健全法制；二是，家族暴富後令後代貪圖安逸；三是，中共為保江山付出的維穩成本之巨大令子孫望而生畏；最後是見識過外國的生活後，不願再回來。因此，這等於「讓中國特權階層的子孫們用腳投了票：不愛江山愛美國」。<br />\n<br />\n文章認為，中共執政者的軟肋在其子孫，「他們可以打壓住臣民，卻抑制不了其親子嫡孫的理性選擇：融入世界，過文明的。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n法廣網"},{"pid":"11f66741e3e9941fc0036bfe3b3922934b4f015c","tid":2130402,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:42:31.000Z","msg":"好簡單道理 ，你會唔會係屠房同廚房食野？"},{"pid":"60f4298d37ef29ae9bdbb1e422becbe139220002","tid":2130402,"uid":93986,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"11f66741e3e9941fc0036bfe3b3922934b4f015c","tid":2130402,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:42:31.000Z","msg":"好簡單道理 ，你會唔會係屠房同廚房食野？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:43:12.000Z","msg":"大陸：屠房<br />\n香港：廚房<br />\n<br />\n西方國家：飯廳"},{"pid":"168c55ac30eef6057ce300289b32b5ec08844c6a","tid":2130402,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60f4298d37ef29ae9bdbb1e422becbe139220002","tid":2130402,"uid":93986,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"11f66741e3e9941fc0036bfe3b3922934b4f015c","tid":2130402,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:42:31.000Z","msg":"好簡單道理 ，你會唔會係屠房同廚房食野？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:43:12.000Z","msg":"大陸：屠房<br />\n香港：廚房<br />\n<br />\n西方國家：飯廳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:43:42.000Z","msg":"屠房就養豬，廚房又熱又有味。"},{"pid":"2c04a8301abaede7b19b833e9b8b536c7aae3260","tid":2130402,"uid":306914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"11f66741e3e9941fc0036bfe3b3922934b4f015c","tid":2130402,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:42:31.000Z","msg":"好簡單道理 ，你會唔會係屠房同廚房食野？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:50:09.000Z","msg":"屠房同廚房係源頭取材，都係堂食，啱啱禁咗，除非你係黑警"},{"pid":"115d22661d82a032a6ca18af2f21a9b85b2ded03","tid":2130402,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c04a8301abaede7b19b833e9b8b536c7aae3260","tid":2130402,"uid":306914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"11f66741e3e9941fc0036bfe3b3922934b4f015c","tid":2130402,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:42:31.000Z","msg":"好簡單道理 ，你會唔會係屠房同廚房食野？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:50:09